author: Zenon Deshaun
text:
All i am reminding myself is that there’s information and knowledge that run’s through our dna 🧬 long before the beginning our time. 

The enemy has done a great job of indoctrinated us for us to retain the truth and actually realize it. Real electric light being’s.

author: Zenon Deshaun
text:
It’s one thing to know yourself, but it’s another to know your roots. To know truth & history. 

We are the blood line from The Most High, children of Sun.

I must learn to do & be better. To open my mind to truth because the truth is vital to my higher self. Pain’s run deep.

author: Zenon Deshaun
text:
Why were we taught that we came from Africa as slaves just because of our skin color rather, it may be from where our ancestors came? 

It’s a lie. The knowledge that is presented though just because our ancestors went through thing’s doesn’t mean our state isn’t relevant today.

author: Zenon Deshaun
text:
7 days of self awareness should be interesting, I’ve been through a lot so I need to learn to be fully aware of one self. 

My focus in life. My goal’s. To the Know Thyself, actually knowing to pay attention to self. She’d light on thy mind. Get that dust out my eye.

author: Zenon Deshaun
text:
So on Friday, New Full Moon ! 🌕 
Ok boom ! 

Set my Intentions & manifest what’s best yet to come.  

Shedding a lot of old limiting beliefs as well. 

Plus it’s in Virgo & that’s my Rising.
 
Everything is changing, giving thanks on this healing process. 🧘🏾‍♂️✨🤎✊🏾💔

author: Zenon Deshaun
text:
Eating different really help’s with my new found mindset. 

Going plant based ain’t so bad after all. 🌱 🪴 

Health is wealth y’all. ✨🤎

author: Zenon Deshaun
text:
It took me a long time to cut out meat, beef, pork, but im glad I did it.
Had to learn how to control my mind. What I’ve came to learn was, if I can’t control what I eat, then I can’t control my mind or anything else. 
Having good high vibrational energy is important to me.🤎✨
